{"tid":1421108,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持香港示威者 美眾議院議長佩洛西發聲明","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:27:09.000Z","uid":176401,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"574105007b0ee69813716ee99c5e0c9d5f62725c","tid":1421108,"uid":176401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/0806/20190806114635196.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F0806%2F20190806114635196.jpg&h=fe574b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國會眾議院議長南希.佩洛西（2019年8月1日）<br />\n<br />\n美國國會眾議院議長南希.佩洛西（Nancy Pelosi）發表聲明，支持充滿勇氣的香港示威群眾。<br />\n<br />\n代表加州的民主黨眾議員佩洛西8月5日晚間在其美西辦公室發表聲明講，入夏以來，香港人民一直到今天，向全世界發出一個激動人心的信息，那就係：自由、正義和民主的理想永遠也不會被威嚇和不公義澆滅。<br />\n<br />\n她講：香港人民表現出了極大的勇氣，同拒絕尊重法治、不願意履行一國兩制義務的懦弱政府，形成了極其鮮明的對比。廿多年前，中共政府承諾要在香港實行一國兩制。香港人民配得上擁有真正自治，而香港基本法和其他相關的國際條約，承諾並保證了香港人民擁有的這種權利。香港立法會早就應採取這樣的措施，響應港人提出的這種合法民主訴求，馬上徹底並永久性撤銷引起極大民怨的&ldquo;逃犯條例&rdquo;修訂工作。<br />\n<img src=\"http://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2019/0806/20190806114636550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2019%2F0806%2F20190806114636550.jpg&h=4e0577e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國會眾議院議長南希.佩洛西8月5日發表聲明，支持充滿勇氣的香港示威群眾。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西議長講：美國國會裡的民主和共和黨人，都同香港人民站在一起，希望他們能擁有一個充滿希望、自由和民主的未來。她講，藍托斯人權委員會的兩位共同主席麥戈文（Jim McGovern）議員和史密斯（Chris Smith）議員，曾向特朗普行政當局發出呼籲，要求停止向香港警方輸出和銷售防暴裝置和設備，我們在呢度重申這種呼籲和要求。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西議員講：我們回到華盛頓之後，參眾兩院的兩黨議員們，將開始工作，推動香港人權和民主法案，為保持香港的民主自由還有法治而努力奮鬥。<br />\n本文網址：<a href=\"http://hk.aboluowang.com/2019/0806/1325445.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2019%2F0806%2F1325445.html&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCt2ufVLooqfEZhiAoxVhWLg%3D&h=e7f0738b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.aboluowang.com/2019/0806/1325445.html</a>"},{"pid":"09d6a0fd9b35bdebde6b304900bd25787d8dfb16","tid":1421108,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"美國國民&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;侵"},{"pid":"ec5aca7f5dd830309788122ea5530616fc51fe03","tid":1421108,"uid":176401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"侵: 打經濟<br />\n國會: 打意識型態 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c09959e3d32ac4cf058ab132c5ecf71e04b11b","tid":1421108,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"除左打飛機好似無乜用途"},{"pid":"88448f673bc2e7fd38e7c28822bf886e520ea9fb","tid":1421108,"uid":276715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:08:19.000Z","msg":"有無用都好 多謝佢多次為香港發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c83d637c76cb4a15f547f80c9f53b7bc3cca96","tid":1421108,"uid":176401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54c09959e3d32ac4cf058ab132c5ecf71e04b11b","tid":1421108,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"除左打飛機好似無乜用途"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:22:38.000Z","msg":"AV 都係用黎打飛機 如果無AV會點?"},{"pid":"8b43245ca5067e84407bf630a783f3c88a2c68cc","tid":1421108,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}